516
01:11:22,174 --> 01:11:26,383
I changed my mind.
I've always liked weddings.

517
01:11:26,675 --> 01:11:30,092
Weren't you gonna see
your sister before the game?

518
01:11:30,342 --> 01:11:33,426
I called her.
She will come to the hotel.

519
01:11:33,426 --> 01:11:36,760
I promised her we will eat at
the restaurant tonight.

520
01:11:36,760 --> 01:11:38,760
