529
01:12:20,892 --> 01:12:24,017
Lydia, trust me,
it's over.

530
01:12:24,767 --> 01:12:27,309
I travelled with Angela.

531
01:12:27,309 --> 01:12:30,976
The excuse was to write
a travel guide.

532
