wedding. She didn't in the end.

551
01:14:16,201 --> 01:14:19,035
It was you she cried for.

552
01:14:21,327 --> 01:14:25,869
She called me to tell me
she cried for me.

553
01:14:27,328 --> 01:14:30,203
