679
01:25:33,223 --> 01:25:36,598
-Are you a relative?
-A friend.

680
01:25:36,723 --> 01:25:40,557
-Marco Zuloaga is my name.
-Can I see your I.D.?

681
01:25:43,433 --> 01:25:47,392
-Can I call him?
-He will call you.

682
01:25:47,683 --> 01:25:51,309
